snippet.title: Mega Man Arena Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Mega Man Arena - the 8bit Fighter you sort-of always wanted is now available!  Download it at http://www.megamanarena.com

Take on the roles of one of nine legendary robot masters, including Mega Man, Quick Man, Flash Man, Metal Man, and more!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/megamanarena/

Discord: https://discord.gg/adTuBsV

DOWNLOAD NOW!  http://www.megamanarena.com
